data.description: The epitome of urban living! This spacious 2 bed, 2 bath Penthouse in the heart of Lincoln Square will change your life. You will love to entertain in the wide open kitchen and great room with space for lounging, room for a dining table, a gas fireplace, and a rare front balcony - perfect for grilling.  Cook up some love in your chef's kitchen with granite countertops, plentiful cabinets, and stainless steel appliances.  Your generous primary suite is large enough for a king-size bed, has a sizable walk-in closet, and a private rear terrace with city views. The wonderful en suite bath has a double bowl vanity, a separate shower, and a Jacuzzi tub.  This incredible unit also includes TWO TANDEM PARKING SPOTS, a full-size in-unit laundry room, a shared rooftop deck, and a private storage locker.   You will be 3 blocks from the EL & Metra & steps to premier dining and shopping. Pet Friendly building -2 pets max.
